9 An Act relating to long-term care referral fees;
amending Section 2, Chapter 58, O.S.L. 2024 (63 O.S.
10 Supp. 2025, Section 1-866.2) which relates to
referral agency referrals; modifying disclosure
11 requirements from referral agencies; amending Section
3, Chapter 58, O.S.L. 2024 (63 O.S. Supp. 2025,
12 Section 1-866.3), which relates to referral agency
restrictions; adding a restriction; amending Section
13 4, Chapter 58, O.S.L. 2024 (63 O.S. Supp. 2025,
Section 1-866.4) which relates to referral agency
14 requirements; modifying the duties for referral
